3.2.95" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. III, 2, 95</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I would not have him miscarry for the half of my d.</quote> <bibl n="shak. tn 3.4.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. III, 4, 70</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>at whose conception nature this d. gave,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 1.1.9" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. I, 1, 9</bibl></cit>.
